	measure 'Total de Faturamento' = ```
			
			
			VAR v = [Total de Consultas Realizadas]
			RETURN
			SWITCH(
			    TRUE(),
			
			    ABS(v) >= 1000000000,
			        "R$ " & FORMAT(v/1000000000, "#,##0.###") & "B",
			
			    ABS(v) >= 1000000,
			        "R$ " & FORMAT(v/1000000, "#,##0.###") & "M",
			
			    ABS(v) >= 1000,
			        "R$ " & FORMAT(v/1000, "#,##0.###") & "k",
			
			    "R$ " & FORMAT(v, "#,##0")
			)
			
			
			```
		displayFolder: Notas Fiscais\Faturamento
		lineageTag: e771adbe-3402-49a9-9cce-2df704f3e2d9

